  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rugösi is a very short game - just like our lives. Professor Alveus and Professor Vox invite you to play through the test chambers and compete against others in the Steam leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Professors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Very short play time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Male/female character option.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes character speeches that some players may find long.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905510/extras/9d085123e84bea7a74e08426c5b7617b.poster.avif?t=1768775215\" width=466 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905510/extras/9d085123e84bea7a74e08426c5b7617b.webm?t=1768775215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905510/extras/9d085123e84bea7a74e08426c5b7617b.mp4?t=1768775215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905510/extras/a9c2ecf6ab040f11dd4df6b0a78b9294.poster.avif?t=1768775215\" width=396 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905510/extras/a9c2ecf6ab040f11dd4df6b0a78b9294.webm?t=1768775215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905510/extras/a9c2ecf6ab040f11dd4df6b0a78b9294.mp4?t=1768775215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
